ttps://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-20cff2c2280aba4e28605bd9794f2daf_hd.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1626077272.310736","card_id":"Q_471759055","target":{"id":471759055,"title":"如何评价张小龙称做 PC 版微信是一种破坏：用户不再相信对方能立即收到消息，因为对方可能不在电脑旁？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/471759055","type":"question","created":1626071062,"answer_count":30,"follower_count":47,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[176,36959,87303,140896,725185],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我们知道，微信早期是没有 PC 版的，即使现在已经有了，也不如手机端好用，每次登录都需要在手机上确认，长时间不登录甚至需要手机端重新扫码。 “微信之父”张小龙在其作品《微信背后的产品观》一书中透露，微信本来不想做 PC 版，因为觉得做 PC 版是一种破坏。但是因为很多用户说在手机里面输入文字太辛苦了，经常坐在计算机旁边，却用手机输入文字。所以微信为了更好地解决输入的问题，做了 Web 版而不是真正的 PC 端。 至于为什么不做 PC 端，张小龙表示：“如果我们去做 PC 版，会带来的结果是：用户不再相信对方能立即收到消息了，因为我们可能发到一台没有人在旁边的计算机上，那么他会选择别的可以很快找到他的工具”。张小龙：做 PC 版微信是一种破坏"},"attached_info":"ClQIkdPl7MizqJsOEAMaCDY3MTE0OTQ0IJbAr4cGMAE4L0Amcgk0NzE3NTkwNTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1626077272.3114061","card_id":"Q_21367029","target":{"id":21367029,"title":"拍纪录片的导演和编导们，你们现在的生活是怎样的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/21367029","type":"question","created":1374423815,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":431,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[61030],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClIIkdPl7MizqJsOEAMaBjcyNzQ2NSCHlrCPBTAAOK8DQCdyCDIxMzY3MDI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-591915b83843851a5c8fca66a0155cef_1440